select 'Todays' idvalue ,'Sysdate - Invoice_Date = 0' id from dual
union
select 'Yesterday' idvalue ,'Sysdate - Invoice_Date = 1' id from dual
union
select 'Last 30 days' idvalue ,'Sysdate - Invoice_Date <=30' id from dual
union
select 'Last 45 days' idvalue ,'Sysdate - Invoice_Date <=45' id from dual
union
select 'Last 60 days' idvalue ,'Sysdate - Invoice_Date <=60' id from dual
union
select 'Last 90 days' idvalue ,'Sysdate - Invoice_Date <=90' id from dual
union
select 'Last 120 days' idvalue ,'Sysdate - Invoice_Date <=120' id from dual
union
select 'Last 180 days' idvalue ,'Sysdate - Invoice_Date <=180' id from dual
union
select '7 days older' idvalue ,'Sysdate - Invoice_Date >= 7' id from dual
union
select '15 days older' idvalue ,'Sysdate - Invoice_Date >= 15' id from dual
union
select '30 days older' idvalue ,'Sysdate - Invoice_Date >= 30' id from dual
union
select '45 days older' idvalue ,'Sysdate - Invoice_Date >= 45' id from dual
union
select '60 days older' idvalue ,'Sysdate - Invoice_Date >= 60' id from dual
union
select '90 days older' idvalue ,'Sysdate - Invoice_Date >= 90' id from dual
union
select '120 days older' idvalue ,'Sysdate - Invoice_Date >= 120' id from dual
union
select '180 days older' idvalue ,'Sysdate - Invoice_Date >= 180' id from dual
union
select 'Invoice with Balances' idvalue ,'Nvl(BAlance_total,0) <> 0 ' id from dual
union
select 'Fully Paid Invoices' idvalue ,'Nvl(BAlance_total,0)  = 0' id from dual
Union
Select 'Supplier Has Email' idvalue,'Supplier_ID in (Select  s.supplier_id from AP_SUPPLIERS s Where s.email is not null) '  id from dual
Union
Select 'Supplier Has No Email' idvalue,'Supplier_ID in (Select  s.supplier_id from AP_SUPPLIERS s Where s.email is  null) '  id from dual
union
select 'Unpaid Invoices Past Due Date' idvalue ,'Balance_Total <> 0 and AP_Pkg.Get_InvoiceDuedate(Sup_Supplier_ID,Invoice_ID) < Trunc(sysdate)' id from dual
union
select 'Unpaid Invoices Past Due Date By 7 days' idvalue ,'Balance_Total <> 0 and (Sysdate - AP_Pkg.Get_InvoiceDuedate(Sup_Supplier_ID,Invoice_ID)) >=7 ' id from dual
union
select 'Unpaid Invoices Past Due Date By 15 days' idvalue ,'Balance_Total <> 0 and (Sysdate - AP_Pkg.Get_InvoiceDuedate(Sup_Supplier_ID,Invoice_ID)) >= 15' id from dual
union
select 'Unpaid Invoices Past Due Date By 30 days' idvalue ,'Balance_Total <> 0 and (Sysdate - AP_Pkg.Get_InvoiceDuedate(Sup_Supplier_ID,Invoice_ID)) >= 30' id from dual
union
select 'Unpaid Invoices Past Due Date By 45 days' idvalue ,'Balance_Total <> 0 and (Sysdate - AP_Pkg.Get_InvoiceDuedate(Sup_Supplier_ID,Invoice_ID)) >= 45' id from dual
union
select 'Unpaid Invoices Past Due Date By 60 days' idvalue ,'Balance_Total <> 0 and (Sysdate - AP_Pkg.Get_InvoiceDuedate(Sup_Supplier_ID,Invoice_ID)) >= 60' id from dual
union
select 'Unpaid Invoices Past Due Date By 90 days' idvalue ,'Balance_Total <> 0 and (Sysdate - AP_Pkg.Get_InvoiceDuedate(Sup_Supplier_ID,Invoice_ID)) >= 90' id from dual
union
select 'Unpaid Invoices Past Due Date By 120 days' idvalue ,'Balance_Total <> 0 and (Sysdate - AP_Pkg.Get_InvoiceDuedate(Sup_Supplier_ID,Invoice_ID)) >= 120' id from dual
union
select 'Unpaid Invoices Past Due Date By 150 days' idvalue ,'Balance_Total <> 0 and (Sysdate - AP_Pkg.Get_InvoiceDuedate(Sup_Supplier_ID,Invoice_ID)) >= 150' id from dual
union
select 'Unpaid Invoices Past Due Date By 180 days' idvalue ,'Balance_Total <> 0 and (Sysdate - AP_Pkg.Get_InvoiceDuedate(Sup_Supplier_ID,Invoice_ID)) >= 180' id from dual

       ,spl.Item_Id,spl.Case_Cp,spl.Unit_Cp,spl.Supplier_Id
       ,spl.Bu_Id,spl.Case_Unit,spl.Reorder_Qty,spl.Delete_Flag
       ,spl.Supplier_Product_Code,spl.Alternate_Case_Cp
       ,spl.Alternate_Unit_Cp,spl.Created_By,spl.Creation_Date
       ,spl.Last_Update_Date,spl.Last_Updated_By,spl.Record_Status
       ,spl.Update_Source,spl.Preference_Code,spl.Supplier_Product_Desc,

       Inv_pkg.GetSupplierName(spl.Supplier_Id) Supplier_name,

Where  il.Item_Id = spl.Item_Id

Union
 select 'inSTOCK >= QtyToPick' IdValue ,'Qty_ToPick_Units >= Qty_ActualInStock and Qty_ActualInStock > 0 ' ID from Dual
Union
 select 'QtyToPick > 0' IdValue ,'Qty_ToPick_Units >0 ' ID from Dual
Union
 select 'QtyToDeliver > 0' IdValue ,'Qty_Delivered_Units > 0 ' ID from Dual
Union
 select 'All Backorders' IdValue ,
'SalOrder_Pkg.Is_itBackOrder(order_Status,Order_Line_Status,Delivery_Status,Qty_toPick_Units,Order_Category_Code) = 1' ID from Dual

 select 'Backorders In Stock' IdValue ,

 select 'Ready To Deliver' IdValue ,'LinePhaseCode='||''''||'READY TO DELIVER'||'''' ID from Dual
Union
 select 'Ready To Pick' IdValue ,'LinePhaseCode='||''''||'READY TO PICK'||'''' ID from Dual
Union
 select 'Picked' IdValue ,'Order_Line_Status='||''''||'PICKED'||'''' ID from Dual
Union
 select 'Not Picked yet' IdValue ,'nvl(Qty_UserPicked_Units,0) = 0' ID from Dual
Union
 select 'Picked But Not Delivered' IdValue ,'nvl(Qty_UserPicked_Units,0) <> Nvl(Qty_Delivered_Units,-1) ' ID from Dual
Union
 select 'Picked Today' IdValue ,'Trunc(Order_Line_Status_Date) = Trunc(Sysdate) and Order_Line_Status ='||''''||'PICKED'||'''' ID from Dual
Union
 select 'Picked Yesterday' IdValue ,'Trunc(Order_Line_Status_Date) = Trunc(Sysdate-1) and Order_Line_Status ='||''''||'PICKED'||'''' ID from Dual

 select 'Delivered Today' IdValue ,'Trunc(Delivery_Date) = Trunc(Sysdate) '  ID from Dual

 select 'Delivered Yesterday' IdValue ,'Trunc(Delivery_Date) = Trunc(Sysdate-1) '  ID from Dual

    ||''''||'PICKED'||'''' ID from Dual

 select 'Created Today' IdValue ,'Trunc(Creation_Date) = Trunc(Sysdate) '  ID from Dual

select il."MAX_QTY",il."MIN_QTY",il."DELETE_FLAG",il."UPDATE_SOURCE",il."LAST_UPDATED_BY",il."LAST_UPDATE_DATE",il."CREATION_DATE",il."BU_ID",il."LOCATION_ID",il."CREATED_BY",il."ITEM_ID",il."RECORD_STATUS",il."QUANTITY",il."AVERAGE_UNITCP",il."LAST_BOUGHT_UNITCP",il."ANNUAL_STKTAKE_BATCH",il."ANNUAL_STKTAKE_DATE",il."INITIAL_STKTAKE_BATCH",il."INITIAL_STKTAKE_DATE",il."OPENING_BALANCE",il."CLOSING_BALANCE",il."QTY_RESERVED",il."QTY_SOLD",il."LAST_ADJUST_DATE",il."LAST_SOLD_DATE",il."LAST_BOUGHT_DATE",il."QTY_RETURNED_TO_SUPPLIER",il."QTY_RETURNED_FROM_CUSTOMER",il."QTY_ADJUSTED",il."QTY_GOODSIN",il."QTY_RESRVED",il."QTY_ALLOCATED",il."QTY_INORDER",il."LAST_PO_QTY",il."LAST_SOLD_QTY",il."QTY_RESERVED_GRN",il."QTY_RESERVED_PO",il."QTY_RESERVED_BALANCE",il."QTY_RESERVED_FULFILLED",il."QTY_RESERVED_INVOICED",il."LAST_PO_DATE",il."LAST_GRN_QTY",il."DEFAULT_SUB_LOCATION_ID",il."QTY_RQSTION",il."QTY_RQSTION_TRANSIT",il."CLASS_CODE_VALUE",il."CLASS_CODE_QUANTITY",il."CLASS_CODE_PICKING" , i.item_number,i.Item_name,i.Picturename,i.picturetype,
       i.Stockable, i.Purchaseable, i.Valuable,i.Case_Unit,
       l.Location_Name,i.Picturename1,i.picturename2,i.picturename3,
       il.Min_Qty Loc_MinQty,il.Max_Qty Loc_MaxQty,
        l.Location_Type,l.Location_Area_Code,
       l.Location_Region_code,l.Location_Number,
       To_Number(To_Char(il.Last_Update_date,'RRRRMMDD')) Daily,
       To_Number(To_Char(il.Last_Update_date,'RRRRWW')) Weekly,
       To_Number(To_Char(il.Last_Update_date,'RRRRMM')) Monthly,
       To_Number(To_Char(il.Last_Update_date,'RRRR')) Yearly,
       To_Number(To_Char(il.Last_Update_date,'RRRRMMDDHH24')) Hourly,
       'Date:'||To_Char(il.Last_Update_date,'DD/MM/RRRR') DailyChar,
       'Week:'||To_Char(il.Last_Update_date,'WW / RRRR') WeeklyChar,
       'Month:'||To_Char(il.Last_Update_date,'Month / RRRR') MonthlyChar,
       'Year:'||To_Char(il.Last_Update_date,'RRRR') YearlyChar,
       'Hour:'||To_Char(il.Last_Update_date,'DD/MM/RRRR HH24AM') HourlyChar,
        Substr(cmn_common_pkg.GetUsername(il.created_by),1,40) OperatorName,
        Cmn_Common_Pkg.GetUserName(il.Created_By) CreatedByUser,
       Cmn_Common_Pkg.GetUsername(il.Last_Updated_By) UpdatedByUser,
       il.Last_Update_Date Report_Date ,
       Inv_pkg.GetSupplierName(i.Sup_Supplier_Id) Supplier_name,
       inv_pkg.getcategoryname(i.iic_category_id) category_name,
       inv_pkg.getsubcategoryname(i.iisc_sub_category_id) sub_category_name,
       i.Sup_Supplier_Id Supplier_Id,
       i.IIC_CateGory_Id CateGory_ID, I.IISC_Sub_Category_Id Sub_Category_ID,
       il.Quantity - nvl(il.Qty_Allocated,0) Qty_Available_Units,
       Floor((il.Quantity - nvl(il.Qty_Allocated,0))/i.Case_Unit) Qty_Available_Cases,
     --  Floor((il.Quantity - nvl(il.Qty_Allocated,0))/i.Case_Unit) Qty_Available,
       Case
           When (il.Quantity - nvl(il.Qty_Allocated,0)) < i.Case_Unit Then
                   Round((il.Quantity - nvl(il.Qty_Allocated,0))/i.Case_Unit,2)
       Else
           Floor((il.Quantity - nvl(il.Qty_Allocated,0))/i.Case_Unit)
       End Qty_Available,
       Price_Pkg.Get_RetailPrice('VAT',i.Item_Id) Price0_IncTax,
       Price_Pkg.Get_RetailPrice('NOVAT',i.Item_Id) Price0_ExlTax
from   inv_item_locations il,
       inv_item_Masters_V i,
       Inv_Locations l
Where  il.Item_Id = i.Item_Id
And    il.Location_ID = l.Location_ID
And    i.Saleable = 'Y'

select c.Category_Name,l.Order_Header_ID, c.Category_Id ,
      Count(1) No_Of_Items
From   Ar_SalesOrder_Lines l, Inv_Item_Masters i, Inv_Item_Categories c
Where l.Item_ID = i.Item_Id
And   i.IIC_Category_Id = c.Category_Id
And   l.Qty_Picked_Units > 0
Group By l.Order_Header_ID, c.Category_Id,  c.Category_Name
UNION ALL
select '(0) ALL Categories' Category_Name, l.Order_Header_ID, 0 Category_Id ,
      Count(1) No_Of_Items
From   Ar_SalesOrder_Lines l
Where    l.Qty_Picked_Units > 0
Group By l.Order_Header_ID
Order by 1

Select s."ATTRIBUTE4",s."ATTRIBUTE3",s."ATTRIBUTE2",s."ATTRIBUTE1",s."CURRENT_STATUS",s."OLD_STATUS",s."SOURCE_OBJECT_ID2",s."SOURCE_OBJECT_ID1",s."SOURCE_OBJECT_NAME",s."CREATION_DATE",s."LAST_UPDATED_BY",s."LAST_UPDATE_DATE",s."STATUS_ID",s."DELETE_FLAG",s."BU_ID",s."CREATED_BY",s."UPDATE_SOURCE",l.Order_Header_Id,l.Order_Line_ID,l.Item_ID,l.Sl_No,l.Item_name,l.t_ItemNumber,l.t_ItemName,
       l.Order_Line_Status
From  Cmn_Object_Statuses s, Ar_SalesOrder_Lines L
Where s.Source_Object_name = 'AR_SALESORDER_LINES'
And   s.Source_Object_Id1  = l.Order_LINE_ID

select round(Sysdate - h.Order_Date) order_Age,h.Order_number,h.Customer_Id,
       h.Order_Header_ID, h.Order_Date, h.Order_Status_Date,h.Order_Status,
       h.Phase_Code, c.Customer_Name, c.Customer_Number,c.Shipto_Address_Line1,
       Order_Type, Order_Category_Code    ,
       SALORDER2_Pkg.Get_ActiveLineCount(h.Order_header_Id) Line_Count,
       SALORDER2_Pkg.Get_LineCountbyStatus(h.Order_header_Id,'PICKED') Picked_Count,
       h.ORIG_SYS_REF_HEADER,
       (Select Count(1) from Ar_SalesOrder_Lines l Where l.Order_Header_ID = h.Order_Header_ID) num_of_Lines
From   Ar_SalesOrder_headers h, Ar_Customers c
Where h.Customer_Id   = c.Customer_ID
Order By 1,2

Select s."ATTRIBUTE4",s."ATTRIBUTE3",s."ATTRIBUTE2",s."ATTRIBUTE1",s."CURRENT_STATUS",s."OLD_STATUS",s."SOURCE_OBJECT_ID2",s."SOURCE_OBJECT_ID1",s."SOURCE_OBJECT_NAME",s."CREATION_DATE",s."LAST_UPDATED_BY",s."LAST_UPDATE_DATE",s."STATUS_ID",s."DELETE_FLAG",s."BU_ID",s."CREATED_BY",s."UPDATE_SOURCE",h.Order_Header_Id,h.Batch_name,h.Order_Type,h.Order_Status,
       h.Order_Category_Code
From  Cmn_Object_Statuses s, Ar_SalesOrder_Headers h
Where s.Source_Object_name = 'AR_SALESORDER_HEADERS'
And   s.Source_Object_Id1  = h.Order_Header_Id

select l.Order_Header_ID, c.Category_Id, s.Sub_Category_Id, c.Category_Name,s.Sub_Category_Name,
      Count(1) No_Of_Items
From   Ar_SalesOrder_Lines l, Inv_Item_Masters i, Inv_Item_Categories c,
       Inv_Item_Sub_Categories s
Where l.Item_ID = i.Item_Id
And   i.IIC_Category_Id = c.Category_Id
and   i.IISC_Sub_Category_Id = s.Sub_Category_ID
Group By l.Order_Header_ID, c.Category_Id, s.Sub_Category_Id, c.Category_Name,s.Sub_Category_Name
Order by c.Category_Name,s.Sub_Category_Name

Select Order_Header_Id,
       Sum(Nvl(Qty_Ordered_Units,0)) Qty_Ordered_Units,
       Sum(Nvl(Qty_Picked_Units,0))  Qty_Accepted_Units,
       Sum(SALORDER_PKG.Get_TotalPicked(Order_Header_ID,Order_Line_ID,'SUM','SALESORDER')) Qty_UserPicked_Units,
       Sum(Nvl(Qty_Delivered_Units,0)) Qty_Delivered_Units,
       Sum(Nvl(Qty_Invoiced_Units,0)) Qty_Invoiced_Units,
       Sum(Nvl(Qty_Cancelled_Units,0)) Qty_Cancelled_Units,
       Sum(Decode(Order_Line_Status,'NEW',1,0)) New_Count,
       Sum(Decode(Order_Line_Status,'APPROVED',1,0)) Approved_Count,
       Sum(Decode(Order_Line_Status,'PICKED',1,0)) Picked_Count,
       Sum(Decode(Order_Line_Status,'INVOICED',1,0)) Invoiced_Count,
       Sum(Decode(Delivery_Status,'CONFIRMED',1,0)) Delivered_Count,
       Sum(Decode(Phase_Code,'READY TO PICK',1,0)) ReadyToPick_Count,
       Sum(Decode(Phase_Code,'READY TO DELIVER',1,0)) ReadyToDeliver_Count,
       Count(Distinct t_OrderNumber) WeOrder_Count,
       Count(Order_Line_ID) Total_Lines
From  Ar_SalesOrder_Lines
Group By Order_Header_ID

Select "UPDATE_SOURCE","DELETE_FLAG","BU_ID","CREATED_BY","CREATION_DATE","LAST_UPDATED_BY","LAST_UPDATE_DATE","BATCH_ID","ORDER_CURRENCY_CODE","PAY_CURRENCY_CODE","OTHER_TOTAL","ADDITIONAL_TOTAL","GROSS_TOTAL","POSTAGE_TOTAL","INSURANCE_TOTAL","DISCOUNT_TOTAL","TAX_TOTAL","NET_TOTAL","LINES_OK","LINES_REJECTED","TOTAL_LINES","PRICE_HINT","USER_STATUS_TEXT","USER_STATUS","IMPORT_TEMPLATE_NAME","LOCATION_ID","ORDER_TYPE","ORDER_CATEGORY_CODE","ORDER_SOURCE","SYSTEM_STATUS_CODE","SYSTEM_STATUS_TEXT","PHASE_CODE","IMPORT_STATUS","IMPORT_DATE","BATCH_NAME","CUSTOMER_NAME","CUSTOMER_NUMBER","CUSTOMER_ID","ORDER_HEADER_ID","ATTRIBUTE4","ATTRIBUTE3","ATTRIBUTE2","ATTRIBUTE1" from AR_SOIMPORT_BATCH

select p.sl_No,p.Pmnt_Method_Id,p.Pmnt_Method,p.Validation_Criteria,p.Cashback_Allowed,p.Active,
       p.Pmnt_Type, p.Charge_Type, p.Charge_Value,0.00 Payment_Amount
From   Cmn_Payment_Methods p
Where  Nvl(p.Active,'Y') = 'Y'
And    Nvl(p.Pay_in,'Y') = 'Y'
And    Nvl(p.Available_to_All,'N') = 'Y'
Order By 1

Select l.Invoice_Header_Id,Invoice_Line_Id,l.Sl_No,
       cr.Qty_Credited,cr.Amount_Credited,
       l.Qty_Invoiced_Units Qty_Invoiced , l.Net_Amount Amount_Invoiced,
       (l.Qty_Invoiced_Units-nvl(cr.Qty_Credited,0)) Qty_Balance,
       (l.Net_Amount - nvl(cr.Amount_Credited,0)) Amount_Balance,
       Concat((l.Qty_Invoiced_Units-nvl(cr.Qty_Credited,0)),
             (l.Net_Amount - nvl(cr.Amount_Credited,0))) Concat_Total,
       i.Item_Number,l.Item_Id,i.Item_Name,l.Su_ID,l.Invoice_Unit_SP
From   AR_Invoice_lines l,INV_ITEM_MASTERS i,
       (Select li.Credit_Invoice_Header_Id,li.Credit_Invoice_Line_Id,
       Sum(Nvl(li.Qty_Invoiced_Units,0)) Qty_Credited,
       Sum(nvl(li.Net_Amount,0)) Amount_Credited
       From Ar_Invoice_Lines li
       Group By li.Credit_Invoice_Header_Id, li.Credit_Invoice_Line_ID ) cr
Where l.Invoice_Header_Id = cr.Credit_Invoice_Header_Id (+)
And   l.Invoice_Line_ID   = cr.Credit_Invoice_Line_ID (+)
And   Concat((l.Qty_Invoiced_Units-nvl(cr.Qty_Credited,0)),
             (l.Net_Amount - nvl(cr.Amount_Credited,0))) <> '00'
And   l.Item_Id = i.Item_Id (+)

Select l.Invoice_Line_Id,l.Invoice_header_Id,l.sl_no,
       l.Item_Id, i.Item_Number,l.Item_Name,l.Qty_Invoiced_Units,l.Invoice_Unit_Sp,
       l.net_amount,l.Tax_rate, l.Tax_Amount,l.Discount_Amount,l.Total_Line_Amount,'N' Selected,
      h.Invoice_Status_date,h.customer_ID,
      to_char(Invoice_status_date,'DD-MON-YYYY HH24:MI:SS') Invoice_Date_Char
From  Ar_Invoice_Lines l, Inv_Item_Masters i, AR_Invoice_Headers h
Where l.Item_ID = i.Item_ID
And   l.Invoice_header_Id = h.Invoice_Header_ID
Order by l.Invoice_Line_ID desc

Select Invoice_header_Id,Customer_Id,Customer_name,Customer_number,Invoice_Number,Invoice_Date,Invoice_Type,Gross_Total,
           Balance_Total,Paid_Amount,
           (Balance_Total - nvl(Paid_Amount,0)) OutStanding_Amount
From    AR_NEWUNPAID_INVOICES_V

Select l.Order_Header_Id, h.Order_Number,Nvl(l.T_OrderNumber,h.Order_Number) t_OrderNumber,
       h.Order_Status,h.Order_Status_Date,Nvl(b.Item_Id,l.Item_ID) Item_ID,b.Parent_BOM_ID,b.Level0_Item_ID,
       l.Qty_Picked_Units,b.Bom_Quantity, Nvl(b.Quantity,l.Qty_Picked_Units) Qty_toPick,
       l.Order_Line_Status
From AR_SALESORDER_LINES l, AR_SALESORDER_HEADERS h,
     Inv_Bom_Trans b
Where h.Order_Header_ID = l.Order_Header_ID
And   l.Item_ID = b.Level0_Item_Id (+)
And   l.Order_Header_Id = b.Order_Header_ID (+)
And   l.Order_Line_ID   = b.Order_Line_Id (+)

Select Distinct l.Order_Header_Id, h.Order_Number,Nvl(l.T_OrderNumber,h.Order_Number) t_OrderNumber,
       h.Order_Status,h.Order_Status_Date,
       ar_pkg.get_customername(h.customer_id) Customer_name
From AR_SALESORDER_LINES l, AR_SALESORDER_HEADERS h
Where h.Order_Header_ID = l.Order_Header_ID

select p."RECORD_STATUS",p."DELETE_FLAG",p."UPDATE_SOURCE",p."LAST_UPDATE_DATE",p."LAST_UPDATED_BY",p."CREATION_DATE",p."CRATED_BY",p."BU_ID",p."SL_NO",p."DEFAULT_VALUE",p."DEFAULT_VALUE_TYPE",p."SQL_QUERY",p."DATATYPE",p."DESCRIPTION",p."PROMPT",p."NAME",p."PARAMETER_ID",p."CREATED_BY",crp.CMP_PARAMETER_ID,
       crp.CMRR_REPORT_ID,crp.SL_NO Report_Param_Slno,crp.ORDER_By   ,
       crp.CRP_ID, nvl(crp.PROMPT,p.prompt) Report_Param_Prompt,
       r.Report_ID, CRP.Default_Value RepParam_DefaultValue
from cmn_report_parameters crp, cmn_parameters p, cmn_Reports R
Where crp.cmp_parameter_id = p.Parameter_ID
And   Crp.CMRR_Report_ID   = r.Report_Id
And   Nvl(r.Report_Group,'SINGLE') = 'SINGLE'
UNION
select p."RECORD_STATUS",p."DELETE_FLAG",p."UPDATE_SOURCE",p."LAST_UPDATE_DATE",p."LAST_UPDATED_BY",p."CREATION_DATE",p."CRATED_BY",p."BU_ID",p."SL_NO",p."DEFAULT_VALUE",p."DEFAULT_VALUE_TYPE",p."SQL_QUERY",p."DATATYPE",p."DESCRIPTION",p."PROMPT",p."NAME",p."PARAMETER_ID",p."CREATED_BY",crp.CMP_PARAMETER_ID,

       crp.CRP_ID, nvl(crp.PROMPT,p.prompt) Report_Param_Prompt,
       r.Report_ID, CRP.Default_Value RepParam_DefaultValue
from   cmn_Report_Set s, Cmn_Reports r,
       cmn_report_parameters crp, cmn_parameters p
Where  s.Parent_Report_Id  	= r.Report_ID

                 Price_Pkg.Get_Sps(i.Item_ID,su.Su_Id,Session_Pkg.GetDelimiter,'BOTH',nvl(Session_Pkg.GetContextValue('EXCHANGE_RATE'),1)) MinSuSps,
                 c.Currency_Code,
                 i.Item_status ,

                 Decode(i.Item_Status,'ACTIVE','1','0') Active_Flag ,
                 nvl(i.Item_Condition,'NEW') Item_Condition,

                 sfn_RemoveSpecialChars1(x.Short_Desc,Session_Pkg.GetContextValue('SUBSTITUTE')) www_ShortDesc,

                    When Session_Pkg.GetContextValue('GET_WWW_ATTRIBUTES') is not null
                      Then
                        ImpExp_Pkg.Get_wwwMapCategoryDesc(i.IISC_Sub_Category_ID,c.Customer_ID)
                   Else Null
                   End WWW_Category,
                 Case
                  When Nvl(Su.Sales_Unit,1) = 1 then
                    i.Web_Expedite_flag
                  else
                    Su.Web_Expedite_flag
                  End Web_Expedite_flag,
                 Case
                    When Session_Pkg.GetContextValue('GET_WWW_ATTRIBUTES') is not null
                      Then
                       ImpExp_Pkg.Get_wwwMapCategoryDesc(i.IISC_Sub_Category_ID,c.Customer_ID,'ATTRIBUTES')
                   Else Null
                   End WWW_Category_Attributes,
                 c.Date_Format,
                'ORATECH' Data_Source,
                sfn_RemoveSpecialChars1(nvl(i.www_barcode_type,x.www_Barcode),
                                Session_Pkg.GetContextValue('SUBSTITUTE')) www_barcode,
                sfn_RemoveSpecialChars1(nvl(i.www_parent_sku,x.www_Parentsku),
                                Session_Pkg.GetContextValue('SUBSTITUTE')) www_parentsku,
                sfn_RemoveSpecialChars1(nvl(i.www_relationship_type,x.www_Relationship_Type),

                sfn_RemoveSpecialChars1(nvl(i.www_variation_theme,x.www_Variation_Theme),
                          Session_Pkg.GetContextValue('SUBSTITUTE')) www_Variation_Theme,
                sfn_RemoveSpecialChars1(nvl(i.www_package_quantity,x.www_size_Color),
                      Session_Pkg.GetContextValue('SUBSTITUTE')) www_Size_Color,
                sfn_RemoveSpecialChars1(nvl(i.www_design_pattern,x.www_Size_Color_Map),
                        Session_Pkg.GetContextValue('SUBSTITUTE')) www_Size_Color_Map,
                nvl(i.www_parentage,x.Www_Parentage) www_parentage,
                i.Item_Size,
                i.Item_Colour,
                Inv_pkg.GetManFName(i.IM_MANF_ID) Brand_Name ,
                Case
                  When Nvl(Su.Sales_Unit,1) = 1 then
                    i.Freight_Name
                  else
                    su.Freight_name
                 End Freight_name,
                nvl(su.Sales_Unit,1) * i.Unit_CP Unit_Cp,
                i.Item_Number Parent_Item_Number,
               Case
                  When Nvl(i.Item_Dimension,'N') = 'Y' Then -1
                  When su.Su_Category = 'SALESUNIT' Then 0
                  When su.Su_Category = 'BOM' and su.Sales_Unit = 1 Then 0
                   Else 1
               End  Su_Derived,
               Nvl(Session_Pkg.GetContextValue('EXCHANGE_RATE'),1) Exchange_Rate,
               x.Max_Publish_Qty,
                Case
                    When Session_Pkg.GetContextValue('GET_WWW_ATTRIBUTES') is not null
                      Then
                       ImpExp_Pkg.Get_wwwMapCategoryDesc(i.IISC_Sub_Category_ID,c.Customer_ID,'4')

                   Inv02_Pkg.Get_FreightPrice(i.Item_ID,su.Su_ID,4,'DEU_EXP') DEU_Freights,
                   Inv02_Pkg.Get_FreightPrice(i.Item_ID,su.Su_ID,4,'UKS') UKS_Freights,
                  i.Creation_Date Item_Creation_Date,
                  i.Last_Update_Date Item_Last_Update_Date,
                  c.Default_Upload_Status,
                  nvl(Session_Pkg.GetContextValue('ITEMBATCHID'),c.Item_Batch_ID) Item_Batch_ID,
                 ImpExp_Pkg.IncludeExclude_ItemBatch(nvl(Session_Pkg.GetContextValue
                          ('ITEMBATCHID'),c.Item_Batch_ID),i.Item_ID,c.Item_batch_Hint) Item_Batch_Hint,
                 Nvl(Session_Pkg.GetContextValue('ITEMBATCHID'),c.Item_Batch_ID) ExcludeInclude_BatchID,
                 Nvl(Session_Pkg.GetContextValue('FILTERCRITERIA'),Filter_Criteria) Filter_Criteria ,
                 stat.Qty_InOrder,
                 c.BILLTO_COUNTRY_CODE,
                 i.www_Package_Quantity,
 		 su.Su_Id,
                Nvl(Inv02_Pkg.Get_SuBomCount(i.Item_Id),0)  BomCount,
                u.Uom_Short_Desc, U.Uom_Short_Desc ||' of '||su.Sales_Unit Su_Bom_Desc ,
                su.Su_Number,
                su.Su_Name,
                su.UOM_ID,
                Sfn_GetCatSubcat(i.Item_Id) CatSubCat
           From  Ar_customers c,
                 AR_cust_Item_Uploads x,
                 Inv_item_masters_VA i,
                 Inv_Item_Categories cg,
                 Inv_Item_Sub_Categories scg,
                 AP_Suppliers sup,
                 Inv_Item_Statuses stat,
                 Inv_Item_Sales_Units su,
                 Cmn_Unit_Of_Measurements u
           Where  c.Customer_Number = Session_Pkg.GetCustomerNumber
           And    c.Customer_Id = x.Customer_ID
           And    x.Upload_Item = 'Y'
           And    x.Item_ID     = i.Item_Id
           And    i.Publish_To_Web = 'Y'
           And    i.IISC_Sub_Category_ID   = scg.Sub_Category_ID
	   And    i.IIC_Category_ID = cg.Category_ID
           And    i.Sup_Supplier_Id = Sup.Supplier_ID
           And    i.Item_Id = stat.Item_Id (+)
           And    i.Item_ID = su.IIM_Item_Id (+)
           and    'BOM'     = su.Su_Category (+)
           And    su.Uom_Id  = 	u.Uom_Id (+)
           And    (Session_Pkg.GetContextValue('INCLUDEBOM') = 'Y' and 1 = 1
                   or
		   Session_Pkg.GetContextValue('INCLUDEBOM') = 'N' and Nvl(su.Sales_Unit,1) = 1
                  )

       h.Invoice_Type,h.Invoice_Source,h.Invoice_Category_Code,
       c.Customer_Id,l.Payment_Line_ID,l.Pmnt_Method_ID,
       p.Gac_Gl_Account_ID,l.Actual_Payment_Amount,l.Payment_line_Status_Date,
       l.Payment_Header_Id,l.Payment_Reference,l.Card_Number,
       p.pmnt_method,h.Shipfrom_Location_Id,h.Terminal_Id,

Where l.Pmnt_method_Id 		= p.Pmnt_Method_Id
and   l.Payment_Line_Status 	= 'APPROVED'
And   l.Invoice_header_ID 	= h.Invoice_Header_ID
And   h.Customer_Id       	= c.Customer_Id
Union All
Select 2,'PURINV',h.Invoice_ID,
       h.Invoice_Status_Date,h.gross_total,h.Batch_Name,
       h.Invoice_Number,s.supplier_Name,s.supplier_Number,
       h.Invoice_Type,h.trans_category,h.trans_category,
       s.supplier_Id,l.Payment_Line_ID,l.Pmnt_Method_ID,
       p.Gac_Gl_Account_ID,l.Payment_Amount,l.Payment_line_Status_Date,
       l.Payment_Header_Id,l.description,l.CHEQUE_NUMBER,
       p.pmnt_method, h.BillTo_Location_Id,null,
       l.Created_By,Cmn_Common_Pkg.Get_AcNameByCode(p.Gac_gl_Account_Id)
From Ap_PAYMENT_lines l, Cmn_Payment_Methods p , ap_Invoice_headers h, ap_Suppliers s
Where l.Pmnt_method_Id 		= p.Pmnt_Method_Id
and   l.Payment_Line_Status 	= 'APPROVED'
And   l.Invoice_ID 		= h.Invoice_ID
And   h.sup_supplier_Id 	= s.supplier_Id
Union All
Select 3,'PAYINOUT',h.payment_ID,
       h.payment_Status_Date,(Select Sum(nvl(li.Payin_Amount,0)+(nvl(li.Payout_Amount,0)*-1)) LineAmount
                              From gl_Payment_Lines li
                             Where li.Payment_Id = h.Payment_Id ) gross_total,h.Batch_Name,
       to_char(h.Payment_Id),h.Payment_Reference, null,
       h.payment_source,h.payment_category,null,
       null,l.Payment_Line_ID,l.Pmnt_Method_ID,
       p.Gac_Gl_Account_ID,(nvl(l.Payin_Amount,0)+(nvl(l.Payout_Amount,0)*-1)) Payment_Amount,l.Payment_line_Status_Date,
       l.Payment_Id,l.payment_reference,l.description,
       p.pmnt_method,h.Location_Id,h.terminal_id,
       l.Created_By,Cmn_Common_Pkg.Get_AcNameByCode(p.Gac_gl_Account_Id)
From  gl_PAYMENT_lines l, Cmn_Payment_Methods p , gl_Payment_Headers h
Where l.Pmnt_method_Id = p.Pmnt_Method_Id
and   l.Payment_Line_Status = 'APPROVED'
And   l.Payment_ID = h.Payment_ID

Select  Cashingup_Id, Pmnt_Method,Pmnt_Method_Id,
        Sum(Payment_Amount) Payment_Amount,Sum(Cashingup_Amount) Cashingup_Amount,
        Sum(Difference_Amount) Difference_Amount
From  Gl_Cashingup_Lines_V
Group By Cashingup_Id,Pmnt_Method,Pmnt_Method_Id
Order By Pmnt_Method

Select 1,'SALINV',h.Invoice_header_ID,h.Invoice_Status_Date,nvl(h.gross_total,h.Grand_Total),
      h.Batch_Name,h.Invoice_Number,c.Customer_Name,
      c.Customer_Number,h.Invoice_Type,h.Invoice_Source,
      h.Invoice_Category_Code,c.Customer_Id
From Ar_Invoice_Headers h, ar_Customers c
Where h.Customer_Id = c.Customer_Id
and   h.Invoice_Status = 'APPROVED'
Union All
Select 2,'PURINV',h.Invoice_ID,h.Invoice_Status_Date,h.gross_total,
      h.Batch_Name,h.Invoice_Number,s.supplier_Name,
      s.supplier_Number,h.Invoice_Type,h.trans_category,
      h.trans_category,s.supplier_Id
From Ap_Invoice_Headers h, ap_suppliers s
Where h.sup_supplier_Id = s.supplier_Id
and   h.Invoice_Status = 'APPROVED'
Union All
Select 3,'PAYINOUT',h.payment_ID,h.payment_Status_Date,
       (Select Sum(nvl(l.Payin_Amount,0)+(nvl(l.Payout_Amount,0)*-1)) LineAmount
        From gl_Payment_Lines l
        Where l.Payment_Id = h.Payment_Id ) gross_total,
      h.Batch_Name,to_char(h.Payment_Id),h.Payment_Reference,
      null,h.payment_source,h.payment_category,
     h.payment_category,null
From gl_payment_headers h
where   h.payment_Status = 'APPROVED'

Select isl.Hierarchy1||Substr(isl.sub_Location,nvl(length(Hierarchy1),0)+1) sub_loc_Sort,
       isl.Sub_Location, i.Item_Id, isl.IL_LOCATION_ID LOCATION_ID, i.Quantity
From   Inv_Item_sub_Locations i, Inv_Sub_Locations isl
where  i.Sub_Location_Id = isl.Sub_Location_ID
and    i.Quantity > 0
And    isl.Pickable = 'Y'

With
 PickLine As
 (
Select l.Order_Header_Id, l.Order_Line_ID,l.Sl_No,i.Item_Number,i.Item_Name,l.Qty_picked_Units ,l.Qty_Ordered_Units,
Nvl(SalOrder_Pkg.Get_TotalPicked(l.Order_Header_ID,l.Order_Line_ID),0) Total_Picked,
Location_Pkg.Get_ItemDefSubLocByGroup(Picked_Location_Id,l.Item_Id) Picked_Sub_Location_Id,
   l.Picked_Location_ID,l.BU_ID,l.Item_ID , l.Last_Update_Date,
l.ORIG_SYS_REF_HEADER, l.ORIG_SYS_REF_LINE,l.Order_Line_Status,l.Phase_Code,l.PO_header_ID,
  i.case_unit, i.IIC_Category_Id Category_Id
From AR_SALESORDER_LINES l, Inv_Item_Masters i
Where l.Item_Id  = i.Item_ID
And   l.Phase_Code in ('READY TO PICK')
)
Select p."ORDER_HEADER_ID",p."ORDER_LINE_ID",p."SL_NO",p."ITEM_NUMBER",p."ITEM_NAME",p."QTY_PICKED_UNITS",p."QTY_ORDERED_UNITS",p."TOTAL_PICKED",p."PICKED_SUB_LOCATION_ID",p."PICKED_LOCATION_ID",p."BU_ID",p."ITEM_ID",p."LAST_UPDATE_DATE",p."ORIG_SYS_REF_HEADER",p."ORIG_SYS_REF_LINE",p."ORDER_LINE_STATUS",p."PHASE_CODE",p."PO_HEADER_ID",p."CASE_UNIT",p."CATEGORY_ID",ItemStatus_Pkg.GetQtyInStock(p.Item_ID,p.Picked_Location_Id,p.Bu_ID,'BULEVEL','STOCK') Group_Stock_Qty,
       Location_pkg.GetSublocationStock(p.Item_Id,p.Picked_Location_ID,p.Picked_Sub_Location_ID) Sub_Location_Stock_Qty,
       INV_Pkg.GetSubLocationName(p.Picked_Sub_Location_Id) Sub_Location_Name,
       Mobile_Pkg.get_SubLocationByHierarchy(p.Picked_Sub_Location_Id) Sub_Loc_Sort,
       p.Qty_Picked_Units - p.Total_Picked To_Be_Picked_Qty,
       BOM_PKG.Is_ABomItem(p.Item_Id) Is_Bom,
       SALORDER_PKG.get_OrderNumberFromID(p.ORIG_SYS_REF_HEADER) Orig_Order_Number,
       SALORDER_PKG.get_OrderNumberFromID(p.Order_header_ID) Order_Number,
       Sysdate-p.last_Update_Date Number_Of_Days,
       floor(((p.Qty_Picked_Units - p.Total_Picked)/p.case_unit)) To_Be_Picked_Qty_case
From PickLine P

Select h.Pallet_number,h.sl_no,b.Box_Id,b.sl_No box_sl_no,b.Box_Name,b.Box_Tag , b.Source_Ref_Id2, l.NoofItems, l.total_qty ,
       h.Source_Ref_Id1,
       Mobile_Pkg.Add_HRef('Print Label',
Mobile_Pkg.BuildReportUrl('RWH_PALLETLABEL01','&P_SOURCEREFID1='||h.Source_Ref_Id1),'_blank') Print_Label_url,
               h.Pallet_Header_Id,b.Last_Update_Date
                     From PALLET_BOXES b, PALLET_HEADERS h,
                          (Select li.Box_Id, Count(1) NoOfItems, Sum(li.Quantity) total_qty
                           From Pallet_Lines li Group By li.Box_ID) l
                    Where b.Box_ID  = l.Box_ID (+)
                    And  b.Pallet_Header_ID  = h.Pallet_Header_ID (+)
                    And   b.Source_Object_ref  = 'SALES ORDER'

Select SubMenuID, SubMenuName, SubMenuDescription,

Select uf."USER_ID",uf."USER_NAME",uf."CR_RESP_ID",uf."READ",uf."WRITE",uf."CUR_DELETE",uf."CM_MENU_ID",uf."MENU_NAME",uf."PARENT_MENU_ID",uf."FUNCTION_ID",uf."FUNC_NAME",uf."FUNC_SHORT_NAME",uf."FUNC_DISP_NAME",uf."FUNC_TYPE",uf."MENU_SL_NO",parent.menu_id SubMenuID, Parent.Menu_name SubMenuName,Parent.Menu_Description
            SubMenuDescription,Parent.Menu_Type SubMenuType,
           Parent.menu_Sl_No SubMenuSlNo,
           Mobile_Pkg.Get_MobileUrl||uf.func_name Function_Url
From  Cmn_User_Functions_V uf, Cmn_Menus parent
Where Func_Type = 'MOBILE'
And   uf.Parent_Menu_Id = Parent.Menu_Id

Select Item_ID,bu_Id,sum(ytd) ytd,sum(lastyear) lastyear ,sum(thismonth) thismonth,
       sum(lastmonth) lastmonth, sum(last3month) last3month,sum(last6month) last6month,sum(last9month) last9month,
       sum(jan) jan, sum(feb) feb, sum(mar) mar,
       sum(apr) apr, sum(may) may, sum(jun) jun, sum(jul) jul, sum(aug) aug,
       sum(sep) sep, sum(oct) oct, sum(nov) nov, sum(dec) dec,
       sum(thisweek) thisweek, sum(week1) week1,sum(week2) week2,sum(week3) week3,
       sum(week4) week4,sum(week5) week5,sum(week6) week6,
       sum(year2) year2,sum(year3) year3,sum(year4) year4,sum(quantity) quantity,
       sum(ytd_val) ytd_val,sum(lastyear_val) lastyear_val ,sum(thismonth_val) thismonth_val,
       sum(lastmonth_val) lastmonth_val, sum(jan_val) jan_val, sum(feb_val) feb_val, sum(mar_val) mar_val,
       sum(apr_val) apr_val, sum(may_val) may_val, sum(jun_val) jun_val, sum(jul_val) jul_val , sum(aug_val) aug_val,
       sum(sep_val) sep_val , sum(oct_val) oct_val , sum(nov_val) nov_val , sum(dec_val) dec_val,
       sum(thisweek_val) thisweek_val, sum(week1_val) week1_val ,sum(week2_val) week2_val ,sum(week3_val) week3_val,
       sum(week4_val) week4_val ,sum(week5_val) week5_val , sum(week6_val) week6_val,
       max(report_date) Report_date
From  (
   Select Item_ID,bu_Id,ytd ytd,lastyear lastyear ,thismonth thismonth,
       lastmonth lastmonth, jan jan, feb feb, mar mar,
       apr apr, may may, jun jun, jul jul, aug aug,
       sep sep, oct oct, nov nov, dec dec,
       thisweek thisweek, week1 week1,week2 week2,week3 week3,
       week4 week4,week5 week5,week6 week6,
       year2 year2,year3 year3,year4 year4,quantity quantity,
       report_date , last3month,last6month,last9month,
       ytd_val,lastyear_val ,thismonth_val,
       lastmonth_val, jan_val, feb_val, mar_val,
       apr_val, may_val, jun_val, jul_val, aug_val,
       sep_val, oct_val, nov_val, dec_val,
       thisweek_val, week1_val,week2_val,week3_val,
       week4_val,week5_val,week6_val
       From Rep_ordItemSales_v
       Where 1 =2
       And  report_date >= sysdate-365
   Union All
    Select  Item_ID,bu_Id,ytd ytd,lastyear lastyear ,thismonth thismonth,
       lastmonth lastmonth, jan jan, feb feb, mar mar,
       apr apr, may may, jun jun, jul jul, aug aug,
       sep sep, oct oct, nov nov, dec dec,
       thisweek thisweek, week1 week1,week2 week2,week3 week3,
       week4 week4,week5 week5,week6 week6,
       year2 year2,year3 year3,year4 year4,quantity quantity,
       report_date , last3month,last6month,last9month,
       ytd_val,lastyear_val ,thismonth_val,
       lastmonth_val, jan_val, feb_val, mar_val,
       apr_val, may_val, jun_val, jul_val, aug_val,
       sep_val, oct_val, nov_val, dec_val,
       thisweek_val, week1_val,week2_val,week3_val,
       week4_val,week5_val,week6_val
       From Rep_ItemSales_v
       Where report_date >=  sysdate-365
  )
Group by bu_Id,Item_Id

       nvl(JAN,0) JAN ,nvl(FEB,0) FEB,nvl(MAR,0) MAR ,Nvl(APR,0) APR ,Nvl(MAY,0) MAY ,Nvl(JUN,0) JUN,
       nvl(JUL,0) JUL ,Nvl(AUG,0) AUG ,Nvl(SEP,0) SEP ,Nvl(OCT,0) OCT ,Nvl(NOV,0) NOV ,Nvl(DEC,0) DEC ,
       nvl(YTD_val,0) YTD_val,nvl(THISMONTH_val,0) ThisMonth_val,nvl(LASTMONTH_val,0) LastMonth_val,
       nvl(THISWEEK_val,0) ThisWeek_val,nvl(WEEK1_val,0) Week1_val,nvl(WEEK2_val,0) Week2_val,
       nvl(WEEK3_val,0) Week3_val,nvl(WEEK4_val,0) Week4_val,nvl(WEEK5_val,0) Week5_val,nvl(WEEK6_val,0) Week6_val,
       nvl(JAN_val,0) JAN_val ,nvl(FEB_val,0) FEB_val,nvl(MAR_val,0) MAR_val ,Nvl(APR_val,0) APR_val ,Nvl(MAY_val,0) MAY_val ,Nvl(JUN_val,0) JUN_val,
       nvl(JUL_val,0) JUL_val ,Nvl(AUG_val,0) AUG_val ,Nvl(SEP_val,0) SEP_val ,Nvl(OCT_val,0) OCT_val ,Nvl(NOV_val,0) NOV_val ,Nvl(DEC_val,0) DEC_val ,
       Decode(QUANTITY,null,'NO','YES') Sales_History,
       i.Supplier_Unit_Cp  Fob_Unit_Price, Inv_Pkg.Get_ItemBarcode('PRIMARYONLY',i.Item_Id) Default_Barcode ,
       nvl(Qty_InPO,0) Qty_InPO

     Inv_Item_Sales_Units su,ap_suppliers sup,  Rep_365daysItemSalesSum_v sl,
     Inv_Item_Prices sp1 , Inv_Item_Prices sp2, Inv_Item_Prices Sp3,
     Inv_Item_Prices Sp4, Inv_Item_Prices Sp5,
     (Select poli.Item_Id, Sum(poli.Qty_Ordered_Units - poli.Qty_GoodsIn) Qty_INPO
      From   PO_Lines poli
      Where  poli.Order_Status = 'APPROVED'
      Group by poli.Item_ID) pol

And   su.Su_ID          = sp2.IIsu_Su_ID
And   sp2.Ipt_PRice_Type_ID = 2
And   su.Su_ID          = sp3.IIsu_Su_ID
And   sp3.Ipt_PRice_Type_ID = 3
And   su.Su_ID          = sp4.IIsu_Su_ID
And   sp4.Ipt_PRice_Type_ID = 4
And   su.Su_ID          = sp5.IIsu_Su_ID
And   sp5.Ipt_PRice_Type_ID = 5
And   i.Item_Id = pol.item_Id (+)

Select  t.Location_Id,t.Item_Id,
                 sum(t.Picking) Picking,
                 sum(t.Quantity) Quantity, Sum(t.Value) value,
               PERCENT_RANK()
                    OVER (PARTITION BY t.Location_Id ORDER BY sum(t.Picking) DESC ) AS p_Pick,
               PERCENT_RANK()
                    OVER (PARTITION BY t.Location_Id ORDER BY sum(t.Quantity) DESC ) AS p_qty,
               PERCENT_RANK()
                    OVER (PARTITION BY t.Location_Id ORDER BY sum(t.value) DESC ) AS p_value
          From (
                select l.Picked_Location_Id Location_Id ,l.Item_Id,Count(1) Picking,
                        Sum(l.Qty_Invoiced_Units) Quantity,
                        Sum(l.Net_Total_After_Discount) value
                From   Ar_Invoice_Lines l
                Where  l.Order_Line_Id is Not Null
                Group By l.Picked_Location_Id,l.Item_Id
                UNION ALL
                select l.Picked_Location_Id Location_Id ,l.Item_Id,Count(1) Picking,
                        Sum(l.Qty_picked_Units) Quantity,
                        Sum(l.Net_Total_After_Discount) value
                From   Ar_SALESORDER_Lines l
                Group By l.Picked_Location_Id,l.Item_Id
               ) t
           Group By t.Location_Id,t.item_Id
           order by 3 desc,4 desc,5 desc

Select  abc."LOCATION_ID",abc."ITEM_ID",abc."PICKING",abc."QUANTITY",abc."VALUE",abc."P_PICK",abc."P_QTY",abc."P_VALUE", i.Item_Number,i.Item_Name,l.Location_Name
From    REP_ABCBySalesBASE_V abc, Inv_Item_Masters i, Inv_Locations l
Where  abc.Item_Id = i.Item_Id
And    abc.Location_ID   = l.Location_Id

       Decode(cmn_Common_Pkg.Get_LookupAttributeValues('MATRIX_REPORT_COLUMNS','AR_PAYMENT',9),
              M.Pmnt_code,payl.Payment_Amount+nvl(payl.Cashback_Amount,0),0) Pmnt_Option9,

select trunc(snapshot_Date) Snapshot_Date,
      Sum(Qty_InStock*Unit_Cp) Opening_Value,min(i.cr) Credit_Value
      , min(i.dr) Debit_Value , Min(i.Movement) Movement_Value ,
     Sum(Qty_InStock*Unit_Cp) + Min(nvl(i.Movement,0)) Closing_Value
from Rep_SnapedStockVal_V  ,
    ( select trunc(ir.Report_Date) Report_Date, sum(nvl(ir.Credit_Quantity,0)*ir.Unit_Cp) cr ,
             Sum(nvl(ir.Debit_quantity,0)*ir.Unit_Cp) dr ,
            Sum( (nvl(ir.Credit_Quantity,0)*ir.Unit_CP) - (nvl(ir.Debit_Quantity,0)*ir.Unit_CP)) Movement
      from REP_ITEM_CRDR_V ir
      Group By trunc(ir.Report_Date)
      ) i
Where Snapshot_Date = i.Report_Date (+)
Group by trunc(Snapshot_Date)
Order By 1

CurrandPrevNumbers AS

       Lag(Curr_Item_Num) OVER (Order By Curr_Item_Num) Prev_Item_Num

     l.Qty_invoiced_Units  * l.Order_Unit_Sp Total_invoiced_Amount,
     l.Qty_cancelled_Units  * l.Order_Unit_Sp Total_cancelled_Amount,
     (l.qty_ordered_units  - nvl(l.qty_invoiced_units,0)) * l.Order_Unit_Sp  Total_Balance_Amount,
     i.Reorder_Qty,i.Enforce_Reorder_Qty,
     i.MIN_Qty, i.max_qty,i.Inner_Qty, i.case_unit,
     l.Order_Line_Status LineStatus, l.Phase_Code LinePhaseCode ,
     SalOrder_Pkg.Get_TotalPicked(l.Order_Header_Id,l.Order_Line_Id,'SUM','SALESORDER')
     Qty_TotalPicked_Units,
     l.t_Ordernumber,l.Qty_Delivered_Units, l.Qty_UserPicked_Units,l.Sl_No,
     l.Delivery_Status,l.Delivery_Date,
     c.Primary_Customer_ID
From AR_SALESORDER_Headers h,
     AR_SALESORDER_LINES  l,
     Inv_Locations il,
     Inv_Sub_Locations isl,
     Ar_Customers c,
     Inv_Item_Masters i,
     inv_item_statuses iis
Where h.order_Header_ID     = l.order_HEADER_ID
And   h.Customer_ID  = c.Customer_ID
And   l.PICKED_LOCATION_ID  = il.Location_ID
And   l.PICKED_SUB_LOCATION_ID = isl.Sub_Location_Id
And   l.Item_Id        = i.Item_Id
and   i.item_id        = iis.item_id

        nvl(sal.SAL_JUL+sal.SAL_AUG+SAL_SEP+

Select h."TRANS_SEQ",h."TRANS_SOURCE",h."ITEM_ID",h."BU_ID",h."LOCATION_ID",h."SUB_LOCATION_ID",h."REPORT_DATE",h."CREDIT_QUANTITY",h."DEBIT_QUANTITY",h."SOURCE_HEADER_ID",h."SOURCE_LINE_ID",h."SOURCE_TYPE",h."SOURCE_INFO1",h."SOURCE_INFO2",h."TRANSGROUP_CODE",h."STOCK_TRANS_TYPE",h."CREATION_DATE",i.Item_Number,i.Item_name,

       Inv_Pkg.GetLocationName(h.Location_Id) Location_Name,
       i.Valuable,Unit_CP,Average_Unitcp,Last_Bought_UnitCP
From   REP_ITEM_MOVEMENTBASE_V h,
       Inv_Item_Masters i,
       Inv_Sub_Locations sl
Where  h.Item_Id = i.Item_ID
And    h.Sub_Location_ID = sl.Sub_Location_ID
and  h.TRANSGROUP_CODE in ('GRN','EXTERNALMOVEMENT','COUNTDIFFQTY')

Select 3,'ITEM MOVEMENT',iml.IIM_Item_ID,imh.Bu_Id,nvl(iml.location_Id,imh.From_Location_ID)
      ,nvl(iml.sub_location_Id,imh.From_Sub_Location_Id),imh.Header_Movement_Status_Date,Null,iml.Quantity
      ,imh.Item_Movement_Header_Id,iml.Item_Movement_Line_ID,imh.Movement_Type,imh.Batch_Name
      ,null,'INTERNALMOVEMENT','DEBIT',iml.Creation_Date
From Inv_Item_Movement_Headers imh,

Where imh.Item_Movement_Header_Id = iml.Iimh_Item_Movement_Header_ID

And   imh.Header_Movement_Status <> 'NEW'

Select 3,'ITEM MOVEMENT',iml.IIM_Item_ID,imh.Bu_Id,nvl(iml.to_location_Id,imh.To_Location_ID)
      ,nvl(iml.to_sub_location_Id,imh.To_Sub_Location_Id),imh.Header_Movement_Status_Date,iml.Quantity,null
      ,imh.Item_Movement_Header_Id,iml.Item_Movement_Line_ID,imh.Movement_Type,imh.Batch_Name
      ,null,'INTERNALMOVEMENT','CREDIT',iml.Creation_Date

And   imh.Header_Movement_Status <> 'NEW'

      ,nvl(iml.sub_location_Id,imh.From_Sub_Location_Id),imh.Header_Movement_Status_Date,null,iml.Quantity

Where imh.Item_Movement_Header_Id = iml.Iimh_Item_Movement_Header_ID

      ,nvl(iml.sub_location_Id,imh.From_Sub_Location_Id),imh.Header_Movement_Status_Date,Null,iml.Quantity
      ,imh.Item_Movement_Header_Id,iml.Item_Movement_Line_ID,imh.Movement_Type,imh.Batch_Name

And   imh.Header_Movement_Status <> 'INTRANSIT'

Select 3,'ITEM MOVEMENT',iml.IIM_Item_ID,imh.Bu_Id,nvl(iml.to_location_Id,imh.To_Location_ID)
      ,nvl(iml.to_sub_location_Id,imh.To_Sub_Location_Id),imh.Header_Movement_Status_Date,iml.Quantity,Null
      ,imh.Item_Movement_Header_Id,iml.Item_Movement_Line_ID,imh.Movement_Type,imh.Batch_Name

Select Item_ID,bu_Id, sum(ytd) ytd, sum(lastyear) lastyear ,
       Sum(Year2) Year2, Sum(Year3) Year3, Sum(Year4) Year4,
       max(report_date) Report_date
From  (
   Select Item_ID,bu_Id,ytd, lastyear lastyear,
           Year2,Year3,Year4,report_date
       From Rep_Itempurchases_v
       Where report_date between To_Date('01-JAN-'||to_Char(to_Number(To_Char(Sysdate,'RRRR'))-4),'DD-MON-YYYY')
                       and  To_Date('31-DEC-'||to_Char(to_Number(To_Char(Sysdate,'RRRR'))),'DD-MON-YYYY')
  )
Group by bu_Id,Item_Id

Select Item_ID,bu_Id, sum(lastyear) lastyear ,
       Sum(Year2) Year2, Sum(Year3) Year3, Sum(Year4) Year4,
       max(report_date) Report_date
From  (
   Select Item_ID,bu_Id,lastyear lastyear,
           Year2,Year3,Year4,report_date
       From Rep_ordItemSales_v
       Where 1 = 2
       and report_date between To_Date('01-JAN-'||to_Char(to_Number(To_Char(Sysdate,'RRRR'))-4),'DD-MON-YYYY')
                       and  To_Date('01-JAN-'||to_Char(to_Number(To_Char(Sysdate,'RRRR'))),'DD-MON-YYYY')
   Union All
    Select  Item_ID,bu_Id,lastyear lastyear,
           Year2,Year3,Year4, report_date
       From Rep_ItemSales_v
       Where report_date between To_Date('01-JAN-'||to_Char(to_Number(To_Char(Sysdate,'RRRR'))-4),'DD-MON-YYYY')
                       and  To_Date('01-JAN-'||to_Char(to_Number(To_Char(Sysdate,'RRRR'))),'DD-MON-YYYY')
  )
Group by bu_Id,Item_Id

        ,null Season,null Gl_Acname,null Pricebreakname,null Pricebreakdesc
         ,report_pkg.IsMinusStock(slq.QUANTITY) Loc_Quantity

        ,null Qty_Returned_To_Supplier,null Last_Bought_Date

        ,report_pkg.IsMinusStock((Nvl(slq.QUANTITY,0)-Nvl(slq.Minus_Quantity,0))) * i.Average_UnitCP Average_Value

Select r."MIN_QTY",r."MAX_QTY",r."REORDER_QTY",r."CASE_UNIT",r."UNIT_CP",r."ITEM_NUMBER",r."BU_ID",r."ITEM_ID",r."ITEM_NAME",r."QTYINSTOCK",r."ALTERNATE_CASE_CP",r."ALTERNATE_UNIT_CP",r."IIC_CATEGORY_ID",r."IISC_SUB_CATEGORY_ID",r."SUPPLIER_ID",r."SUPPLIER_NAME",r."CATEGORY_NAME",r."SUB_CATEGORY_NAME",r."TAXRATE",r."MANUFACTURER",r."CONTAINER",r."SEASON",r."GL_ACNAME",r."PRICEBREAKNAME",r."PRICEBREAKDESC",r."LOC_QUANTITY",r."QTY_INSTOCK",r."QTY_INORDER",r."QTY_ALLOCATED",r."QTY_RESERVED",r."QTY_GOODSIN",r."QTY_ADJUSTED",r."QTY_RETURNED_FROM_CUSTOMER",r."QTY_RETURNED_TO_SUPPLIER",r."LAST_BOUGHT_DATE",r."LAST_SOLD_DATE",r."LAST_ADJUST_DATE",r."LOCATION_ID",r."FC_UNITCP",r."LOCATION_NAME",r."LAST_BOUGHT_VALUE",r."AVERAGE_VALUE",r."BASE_VALUE",r."BASE_FC_VALUE",r."LAST_BOUGHT_UNITCP",r."AVERAGE_UNITCP",r."ITEM_VALUABLE",r."SL_QUANTITY",r."SL_MINQTY",r."SL_MAXQTY",r."SUB_LOCATION",r."DESCRIPTION",r."SUB_LOCATION_TYPE",r."SL_VALUABLE",r."ITEM_STOCKABLE",r."SL_STOCKABLE",r."MINUS_QUANTITY",r."ACTUALMINUSSTOCK",r."SUB_LOCATION_ID",r."NET_INGREDIENT",r."SUB_LOC_QUANTITY",r."TOTAL_STOCK",r."ITEM_DIMENSION_TYPE",r."SUPPLIER_PRODUCT_CODE" , Inv_Pkg.Get_SuBin(r.Item_ID) Bin_Identifier

Select snap.Location_Id,l.Location_Name
        ,snap.Snapshot_year,Snap.Snapshot_Month
        ,Snap.Identifier1
        ,Sum(Snap.Record_Value) Record_Value
 From  INV_MONHLYREVIEW_VAL_SNAP snap,
       Inv_Locations l
 Where snap.Location_ID = l.Location_ID
 Group By Snap.Location_ID,l.Location_Name
          ,Snap.Snapshot_Year,Snap.Snapshot_Month
          ,Snap.Identifier1

Select snap.Location_Id,l.Location_Name
        ,snap.Sub_Location_ID,sl.Sub_Location
        ,snap.Snapshot_year,Snap.Snapshot_Month
        ,Snap.Identifier1
        ,Sum(Snap.Record_Value) Record_Value
 From  INV_MONHLYREVIEW_VAL_SNAP snap,
       Inv_Locations l,
       Inv_Sub_Locations sl
 Where snap.Location_ID = l.Location_ID
 And   snap.Sub_Location_Id = sl.Sub_Location_ID
 And   snap.Location_Id     = sl.IL_Location_ID
 Group By Snap.Location_ID,l.Location_Name
          ,snap.Sub_Location_Id,sl.Sub_Location
          ,Snap.Snapshot_Year,Snap.Snapshot_Month
          ,Snap.Identifier1

Select Snap.Period_Name,Snap.Period_Line_ID
        ,snap.Location_Id,l.Location_Name
        ,snap.Snapshot_year,Snap.Snapshot_Month
        ,Sum(snap.Open_Value_Base) Open_Value_Base
        ,Sum(Snap.Open_Value_Average) Open_Value_Average
        ,Sum(Snap.Open_Value_LastBought) Open_Value_LastBought
        ,Sum(snap.Movement_Value_Base) Movement_Value_Base
        ,Sum(Snap.Movement_Value_Average) Movement_Value_Average
        ,Sum(Snap.Movement_Value_LastBought) Movement_Value_LastBought
        ,Sum(snap.Close_Value_Base) Close_Value_Base
        ,Sum(Snap.Close_Value_Average) Close_Value_Average
        ,Sum(Snap.Close_Value_LastBought) Close_Value_LastBought
        ,Inv_Pkg.LocItemCategoryVal(Snap.Location_Id,'A CLASS','AVERAGE')
          Average_AClass
        ,Inv_Pkg.LocItemCategoryVal(Snap.Location_Id,'B CLASS','AVERAGE')
          Average_BClass
        ,Inv_Pkg.LocItemCategoryVal(Snap.Location_Id,'C CLASS','AVERAGE')
          Average_CClass
 From  INV_SUBLOC_VAL_SNAP snap,
       Inv_Locations l
 Where snap.Location_ID = l.Location_ID
 Group By Snap.Period_Name,Snap.Period_Line_ID
        ,Snap.Location_ID,l.Location_Name
          ,Snap.Snapshot_Year,Snap.Snapshot_Month

Select Snap.Period_Name,Snap.Period_Line_ID
        ,snap.Location_Id,Snap.Sub_Location_ID
       ,snap.Open_Value_Base,Snap.Open_Value_Average
        ,Snap.Open_Value_LastBought
        ,snap.Movement_Value_Base,Snap.Movement_Value_Average
        ,Snap.Movement_Value_LastBought,Snap.Bu_ID
        ,snap.Close_Value_Base,Snap.Close_Value_Average
        ,Snap.Close_Value_LastBought
        ,Snap.Snapshot_Month,Snap.Snapshot_Year
       ,To_Number(To_Char(snap.creation_date,'RRRRMMDD')) Daily,
       To_Number(To_Char(snap.creation_date,'RRRRWW')) Weekly,
       To_Number(To_Char(snap.creation_date,'RRRRMM')) Monthly,
       To_Number(To_Char(snap.creation_date,'RRRR')) Yearly,
       To_Number(To_Char(snap.creation_date,'RRRRMMDDHH24')) Hourly,
       'Date:'||To_Char(snap.creation_date,'DD/MM/RRRR') DailyChar,
       'Week:'||To_Char(snap.creation_date,'WW / RRRR') WeeklyChar,
       'Month:'||To_Char(snap.creation_date,'Month / RRRR') MonthlyChar,
       'Year:'||To_Char(snap.creation_date,'RRRR') YearlyChar,
       'Hour:'||To_Char(snap.creation_date,'DD/MM/RRRR HH24AM') HourlyChar
       ,Snap.Creation_Date Report_Date
       ,l.Location_Name,sl.Sub_Location,sl.Sub_Location_Type
       ,sl.Sub_Loc_Group_CODE,snap.GROUPEDBY1_VALUE
       ,snap.GROUPEDBY2_VALUE,snap.GROUPEDBY3_VALUE
 From  INV_SUBLOC_VAL_SNAP snap,
       Inv_Locations l,
       Inv_Sub_Locations sl
 Where snap.Location_ID = l.Location_ID
 And   Snap.Sub_Location_ID = sl.Sub_Location_Id
 And   l.Location_ID        = sl.IL_Location_ID

       sum(apr) apr, sum(may) may, sum(jun) jun, sum(jul) jul, sum(aug) aug,
       sum(sep) sep, sum(oct) oct, sum(nov) nov, sum(dec) dec,
       sum(thisweek) thisweek, sum(week1) week1,sum(week2) week2,sum(week3) week3,
       sum(week4) week4,sum(week5) week5,sum(week6) week6,

Select 'ItemNumber|ItemName|CaseQty||InnerQty|ManfName|'||
       'CustomerNote1|CustomerNote2|CustomerNote3|TechSpecs|'||
       'Barcode|SP4|Purchase|NetWeight|GrossWeight|Length|Width|Height|'||
       'KeyWords|PublishToWeb|ItemStyle|ItemFitting|WhoseFor' String,
       0 Item_ID, '0' Item_Number
From Dual
Union ALL
select i.Item_number||'|'||
       SFN_REMOVESPECIALCHARS1(i.Item_Name)||'|'||
       i.Case_Unit||'|'||
       i.Inner_Qty||'|'||
       m.Manf_name||'|'||
       SFN_REMOVESPECIALCHARS1(i.Customer_Notes1)||'|'||
       SFN_REMOVESPECIALCHARS1(i.Customer_Notes2)||'|'||
       SFN_REMOVESPECIALCHARS1(i.Customer_Notes3)||'|'||
       SFN_REMOVESPECIALCHARS1(i.Technical_Specs)||'|'||
       nvl(b.Barcode,i.Item_Number)||'|'||
       Price_Pkg.Get_SUSP(i.Item_Id,Null,4)||'|'||
       i.Purchaseable||'|'||
       i.Net_Unit_Weight||'|'||
       i.Gross_Unit_Weight||'|'||
       i.Unit_Length||'|'||
       i.Unit_width||'|'||
       i.Unit_height||'|'||
       SFN_REMOVESPECIALCHARS1(i.key_words)||'|'||
       i.publish_to_web||'|'||
       i.Item_style||'|'||
       i.item_coloUr||'|'||
       i.item_Size||'|'||
       i.Item_Fitting||'|'||
       i.Whose_For||'|' String,
       i.Item_Id,
       i.Item_Number
From Inv_Item_Masters i , Inv_Manufacturers m,
     (Select  bi.Iim_Item_ID, max(bi.Barcode) barcode
      From   Inv_Item_Barcodes bi
      Where  Length(bi.Barcode) in (14,13,12)
      Group by bi.Iim_Item_ID
      ) b
Where i.IM_Manf_Id = m.Manf_Id (+)
And   i.Item_Number like 'CT%'
And   i.Item_ID     = b.iim_Item_Id (+)
Order By 3

select i.Item_number,
       i.Item_Name,
       i.Case_Unit,
       i.Inner_Qty,
       m.Manf_name,
       i.Customer_Notes1,
       i.Customer_Notes2,
       i.Customer_Notes3,
       i.Technical_Specs,
       Inv_Pkg.Get_ItemBarcode('PRIMARY',i.Item_Id) Primary_Barcode,
       Price_Pkg.Get_SUSP(i.Item_Id,Null,4) sp4_Net,
       i.Purchaseable,
       i.Net_Unit_Weight,
       i.Gross_Unit_Weight,
       i.Unit_Length,
       i.Unit_width,
       i.Unit_height,
       i.key_words,
       i.publish_to_web,
       i.Item_style,
       i.item_coloUr,
       i.item_Size,
       i.Item_Fitting,
       i.Whose_For
From Inv_Item_Masters i , Inv_Manufacturers m
Where i.IM_Manf_Id = m.Manf_Id (+)
And   i.Item_Number like 'CT%'

Select p."RECORD_STATUS",p."UPDATE_SOURCE",p."DELETE_FLAG",p."BU_ID",p."CREATED_BY",p."CREATION_DATE",p."LAST_UPDATED_BY",p."LAST_UPDATE_DATE",p."PALLET_VOLUME",p."PALLET_HEIGHT",p."PALLET_WIDTH",p."PALLET_LENGTH",p."PALLET_WEIGHT",p."UNIT_DESC",p."NO_OF_UNITS",p."ATTRIBUTE4",p."ATTRIBUTE3",p."ATTRIBUTE2",p."ATTRIBUTE1",p."EXT_REF_ID3",p."EXT_REF_ID2",p."EXT_REF_ID1",p."SOURCE_OBJECT_REF",p."SOURCE_REF_ID2",p."SOURCE_REF_ID1",p."PC_ID",p."GRN_ID",p."INVOICE_HEADER_ID",p."ORDER_HEADER_ID",p."CURRENT_LOCATION_ID",p."CURRENT_SUB_LOCATION_ID",p."SUB_LOCATION_ID",p."LOCATION_ID",p."PALLET_HEADER_STATUS_DATE",p."PALLET_HEADER_STATUS",p."PALLET_AGE",p."ACTIVE",p."PALLET_DECRIPTION",p."PALLET_TAG",p."PALLET_DESTINATION",p."PALLET_SOURCE",p."PALLET_TYPE",p."PALLET_DATE",p."PALLET_NUMBER",p."PALLET_NAME",p."PALLET_HEADER_ID",p."SL_NO",p."DISPATCHED_ON",p."DISPATCH_ID",c.Customer_Name,c.Customer_Number,c.Customer_ID,
       Pallet_Pkg.Get_PalletWeightVolume('WEIGHT',p.Pallet_Header_ID) PalletWeight
From  PALLET_HEADERS p, AR_SALESORDER_HEADERS s, AR_CUSTOMERS c
Where p.Dispatch_Id is Not Null
And   p.Source_Object_Ref = 'SALES ORDER'
And   p.Source_Ref_Id1    = s.Order_Header_ID
And   s.Customer_ID       = c.Customer_ID

Select "LANGUAGE_CODE","RECORD_STATUS","UPDATE_SOURCE","DELETE_FLAG","BU_ID","CREATED_BY","CREATION_DATE","LAST_UPDATED_BY","LAST_UPDATE_DATE","SL_NO","ATTRIBUTE6","ATTRIBUTE5","ATTRIBUTE4","ATTRIBUTE3","ATTRIBUTE2","ATTRIBUTE1","ACTIVE","DATE_ACTIVE_TO","DATE_ACTIVE_FROM","SUB_CATEGORY","CATEGORY","SOURCE_NODE_PATH","SOURCE_NODE_ID","WWW_NODE_ID","WWW_SUB_SOURCE_ID","WWW_SOURCE_ID" from WWW_NODES

Select "RECORD_STATUS","UPDATE_SOURCE","DELETE_FLAG","BU_ID","CREATED_BY","CREATION_DATE","LAST_UPDATED_BY","LAST_UPDATE_DATE","ATTRIBUTE6","ATTRIBUTE5","ATTRIBUTE4","ATTRIBUTE3","ATTRIBUTE2","ATTRIBUTE1","ACTIVE","DATE_ACTIVE_TO","DATE_ACTIVE_FROM","WWW_SOURCE_DESC","WWW_SOURCE_NAME","WWW_SOURCE_ID" from WWW_SOURCES
